<td class="mbox-text" style=""><span class="mbox-text-span">It has been suggested that <i><a href="Convergence_(telecommunications)" title="Convergence (telecommunications)">Convergence (telecommunications)</a></i> be <a href="Wikipedia_Merging" title="Wikipedia:Merging">merged</a> into this article or section. (<a href="Talk_Technological_convergence#Merge_from_Convergence_.28telecommunications.29" title="Talk:Technological convergence">Discuss</a>) <small><i>Proposed since March 2011.</i></small> </span></td>
